Day 78: Jenkins Conditional Pipeline

Date: November 30, 2025
Overview
Implemented conditional logic in pipelines.
Key Concepts Learned

When conditions
Branch-based execution
Parameter-based conditions
Environment-based decisions

Jenkinsfile
groovystage('Deploy to Production') {
    when {
        branch 'main'
        environment name: 'DEPLOY_ENV', value: 'production'
    }
    steps {
        sh './deploy-prod.sh'
    }
}

Challenges Faced
Complex condition combinations and ensuring safety for production deployments.
